data.description: Well appointed and large home with 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms! This property has many great features and offers a tremendous amount of space. As you make your way up front, you'll note the tasteful white brick exterior. Inside, you step into a well-lit foyer that opens into a living room that offers vaulted ceilings, built-in bookcases, and fireplace. The galley kitchen overlooks the living space and provides ample cabinet and counter space along with a breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Two dining options are available with a formal dining space along with a breakfast nook. The master suite is located downstairs and provides tons of space, a large walk-in closet, and a separate shower and garden tub. Two additional bedrooms are located downstairs with one that features and on-suite bath that opens to the back porch. Making your way upstairs, you will find two additional bedrooms - one that could be used as a bonus room - that share an jack-and-Jill bathroom. Out back, you will find a covered patio that overlooks an elegant in-ground pool with 1-year old liner that is fully screened. Enjoy entertaining or relaxing with the large outdoor space while also having plenty of yard space for green area. Additional features include two car garage, exterior gutters, and so much more!
